paragraph_1: Hello! I'm Chandranshu Rao, but I mostly go by Anshu. I'm a software engineer based out of the Austin, TX area. I enjoy hacking things together and building apps that make lives easier.
paragraph_2: After I graduated with a B.S in Computer Science from the University of Texas at Dallas, I joined the Google Cloud team in Austin, TX. At Google Cloud, I continue my passion of making cool things that live on the Internet.
